  <fr:p>As soon as the co-span <fr:tex>{ \mathopen {} \left \{ u  \hookrightarrow  u+v  \hookleftarrow  v \right \} \mathclose {}}</fr:tex> is independent, it evidently satisfies the universal property of <fr:link
